Class Pair

  • java.lang.Object
    • cpsc3720.contactserver.Pair

  • public class Pair
extends java.lang.Object
    Pair is a convenience object for sending and returning x,y coordinates. Pair should NOT be used across the client-server divide. Safe only for use internal to client or server.
    Author:
    Matthew Higgins
